-- 02_revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
SELECT
    COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unattributed') AS channel,
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')          AS city,
    SUM(t.amount)                        AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(*)                             AS transaction_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id)        AS unique_customers
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN customer_channel cc USING (customer_id)
LEFT JOIN stores s USING (store_id)
GROUP BY
    COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unattributed'),
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
